components.queue

Interface QueueKernel<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Standard<Queue<T>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Queue<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Queue1L, QueueDL, QueueSecondary

    public interface QueueKernel<T>
extends Standard<Queue<T>>
    Queue kernel component containing method headers and contracts for all methods that will directly interact with the label representations of all Queue implementations. All sub-interface methods should use only these methods to perform operations on the Queue.
    Author:
    Matthew Shoemaker
